short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Search webpages for content for webhooks and send a delete request to each of them

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Want to delete discord webhooks you find with little effort? This extension loads on each page request but does nothing until you hit the delete key. It will then search through the page and nuke any webhook it finds
